    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a flawless factory finish, free of any imperfections, swirls, or chips, and has been kept under a cover in a climate-controlled garage. The interior is equally immaculate, with the scent of fresh leather and absolutely no signs of wear on the bolsters, buttons, or touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio and a spotless engine bay. It delivers a tight, responsive driving experience exactly as the engineers intended. From the crystal-clear glass to the untouched alloy wheels, every detail has been preserved with obsessive care. This is a turn-key investment for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
