      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to list this absolute gem. Seriously, it's in such incredible shape, it feels like it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014spotless inside and out, and it drives perfectly. I'm relatively new to selling here, but I'm more than happy to chat, send more photos, or show you the car whenever you're ready. This is a rare find you won't want to miss!",
